And when they hear what has been revealed to the Messenger, you see their eyes overflowing with tears. They say, "Our Lord, we have believed, so write us down among the witnesses."
And what is it that we do not believe in Allah and the truth that has come to us, so that our Lord will admit us with the righteous people?
Then Allah will admit them to gardens beneath which rivers flow, wherein they will abide therein forever. That is the reward of the righteous.
But those who disbelieved and deny Our Ayat (proofs, evidences, verses, lessons, signs, revelations, etc.), they are the dwellers of the Fire.
O you who believe! Do not make lawful for the good things which Allah has made lawful for you, and do not commit aggression; surely Allah does not love the transgressors.
And eat of what Allah has provided for you and eat for you, and fear Allah in Whom you believe.
